TransAmerican Natural Gas said itreceived approval from a U.S. District Court in Texas allowingthe company to solicit creditor acceptance of its negotiatedChapter 11 plan of reorganization.    The company said the approval authorized the company todistribute the disclosure statement to its creditors andsolicit creditors' acceptance of the plan.    TransAmerican said the confirmation hearing is scheduledfor August 17 in U.S. Southern District of Texas court.    Reuter&#3;